@baseUrl = http://localhost:5121
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================
### SMOKE TESTS - FindingTheSquad API
### ============================================

### 1. REGISTER - Skapa ny användare
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "kyle.ren@gmail.com",
  "username": "kylo_ren",
  "password": "kyloren123!"
}

###

### 2. LOGIN - Logga in och få token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "kyle.ren@gmail.com",
  "password": "kyloren123!"
}

###

### 3. CREATE LFG SESSION - Skapa en LFG session (kräver autentisering)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lfg
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..-pVRFLKTZikWhqCiKU4v0Npi1c3gG0OAYWY1JSZ3FNE


{
  "playerName": "TestPlayer",
  "gameTitle": "Valorant",
  "discordTag": "TestPlayer#1234",
  "description": "Letar efter 2 stycken för rankad play"
}

###

### 4. GET ALL LFG SESSIONS - Hämta alla sessioner
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lfg
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..-pVRFLKTZikWhqCiKU4v0Npi1c3gG0OAYWY1JSZ3FNE

###

### 5. GET ALL USERS - Hämta alla registrerade användare
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/users

###

### 6. GET ALL LFG SESSIONS - Hämta alla sessioner
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lfg
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..-pVRFLKTZikWhqCiKU4v0Npi1c3gG0OAYWY1JSZ3FNE

### ============================================
### SMOKE TEST INSTRUKTIONER:
### ============================================
### 1. Starta API: cd src/backend/FindingTheSquad.WebApi && dotnet run
### 2. Kör #1 (Register) - Notera svaret
### 3. Kör #2 (Login) - Kopiera "token" från svaret
### 4. Sätt token i #3 och #4 vid "Authorization: Bearer"
### 5. Kör #3 (Create) - Ska returnera ID
### 6. Kör #4 (Get All) - Ska returnera lista med sessioner
###
### Alla ska returnera 200 OK!
### ============================================
